{"tid":2055151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際線抗爭動畫上線啦","createTime":"2020-06-07T17:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T00:41:12.000Z","uid":221610,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"78346be7462506b432bdffde911a0cdefa9f16ba","tid":2055151,"uid":221610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T17:26:13.000Z","msg":"諗左好耐，知道國安法前夕大家覺得做到嘅野可能唔多，我希望用呢段抗爭動畫為香港係咁困難嘅時間出一分力。<br />\n<br />\n近日制裁措施及各國紛紛反對國安法，顯示全球對付中共爪牙既決心大增，反共陣營逐漸成形，商家及政界都開始意識到繼續任由中共擺佈會造成危機，希望大家食住個勢，可以幫手係Twitter 上轉發呼籲各國一齊齊心形成反共戰線，connect更多唔同國家嘅人對準中共政權。<br />\n<br />\n希望仲有機會再出，呢個只係上集，大家加油。<br />\n<br />\n粵語: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/5AbthZbXSxI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5AbthZbXSxI&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=bcbba330\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5AbthZbXSxI</a><br />\n<br />\nEnglish: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/OJb1sWp6Bh4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOJb1sWp6Bh4&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=355f5d15\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OJb1sWp6Bh4</a><br />\n<br />\n普通話: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/xJz5lWFEVGA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxJz5lWFEVGA&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=526fe28c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xJz5lWFEVGA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/foNyw3x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfoNyw3x.jpg&h=28839f67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGYU0WT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGYU0WT.jpg&h=b6a33c5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yZU85oy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZU85oy.jpg&h=aa3ca37d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f10df0c43c42fcac3c0676817471ff38de35e2ba","tid":2055151,"uid":204272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T17:27:54